libpam-blue (0.9.0-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * New maintainer (Closes: #580313).
  * Bump Debian Policy up to 3.8.4 (no changes needed).
  * Stick to dpkg-source 3.0 (quilt) format. 
  * Few minor package modifications:
    - Better handler of errors on cleaning targets.
    - Point to correct GPL-2 license file.
    - Switched to UTF8 copyright symbol.
    - Fix on watch file (Notice: upstream download page seems offline).

